docs {
  ## Get Cluster
  ดึงข้อมูลคลัสเตอร์รายการเดียวตาม ID

  Retrieves the full details of a specific hotel chain or company organization, including its business units, license limits, and configuration.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Cluster ID |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  Platform admin only — managed at Keycloak realm role level

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "code": "CL-001",
      "name": "Blueledgers Hotel Group",
      "alias_name": "BLG",
      "is_active": true,
      "max_license_bu": 10,
      "logo_url": null,
      "created_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 404 | Cluster not found |
}

